01:06:28,690 --> 01:06:31,820
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}The story of this kingdom is a powerful one.

718
01:06:31,900 --> 01:06:34,360
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}My dad rallied your forces

